org: estagiario
app: serverless-estagiario
service: serverless-estagiario

plugins:
  - serverless-offline

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs20.x
  logs:
    restApi: false

functions:
  main:
    handler: dist/main.handler
    events:
      - http:
          method: ANY
          path: /
      - http:
          method: ANY
          path: '{proxy+}'
      - http:
          method: POST
          path: webhook
      - http:
          method: GET
          path: webhook
